# Vue implementation rules

- Use Vue 3 Single File Components with JavaScript.
- Use Vue Router for navigation.
- Route pages belong in `src/views`; reusable UI belongs in `src/components`.
- Components must not call Axios directly. Use `src/services`.
- Use CSS variables from `src/styles/tokens.css`; do not hardcode design values.
- Prefer scoped CSS and semantic HTML.
- Reuse existing Base components.
- Do not add Pinia, Tailwind, UI frameworks or icon packages without explicit approval.
- Implement loading, empty, error and disabled states.
- Do not store or log post passwords.
